      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad runnaja wiꞥſch arri-\ndsan ar teem Wihreem no Pnue-\nta/ fazzidains: Kad es ar Meern\nutgreeſifchohs / tad pohſtischu es\nbuhs Maiſi doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Sebus un Zalmunus\nbija eekſch Karkora / un wiꞥnu\nKarra-Spehki pee winneem/ rah-\ndi peezpadeſmits tuhkſtoſchi / kaß\nwiſſi bija atliffuschi no wiﬀa\nSpehka to Behrnu no Rihta puſ-\nfes/ jo ţimts un diwideſmits tuhk-\nſtoſchi Wihri bija bohja gahjuſchi/\nkaß to Sohbinu iſwilke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gideans zehlahs us\nangſchu pa to Zettu to/ kaß Zeltis\ndsihwoja/prett Rihteem no No-\nbas un Jagbeas / un kaue to\nKarra-Spehku / jo taß Karra-\nSpehks gulſeja tur itt drohſcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sebus un Zalmunus\nbehdſe / bet wiꞥſch dsinnahs teem\npakkat / un jaguhſtija tohs diwi\nMidijaniteu Rehnitus/to Sebu\nun Zalmunu / un iſbaidija wiﬀu\nto Karra-Spehku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gideans Joafa Dehls\natgreeſahs no Kaufchanas/pirms\nka ta Saule uſlehze.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad faguhſtija wiꞥſch wee-\nnu Puuti no Sukota Wibreem/\nun waizaja to / un tas uſrakſtija\nwinnam tohs Wirfneekus no Su-\nkota/ un winna Wezzajus ſeptin-\ndeſmits ſeptin Wihrus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahze wiꞥſch pee teem\nWihreem no Sukota/ un fazzija:\nReds / ſche irr Sebus un Zalmu-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nehme ta Pils\nfahta Wezzajus / un Ehrſſchkus\nno Tuksneſeg/ un Dadſchus/ un\npahrmahzija tohs Wihrus n\nSukota.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Tohrni no Pnuek\npohſtija wiꞥſch / un nokawe t\nPilsſahta Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to fazzija wiꞥſch u\nSebu un Zalmunu / kaß tee bija\npar Wihreem / ko juhs Tahbor\nnokawat? un tee fazzija : itt k\nitu / ta bija winni weenada wa\nġa/ itt ta Rehnina Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch:tee bija\nmanni Brahti/ mannas Mahte\nDehli/tik teescham/ ka tas KUNG\ndsihwo/buhntu juhs tohs dsihwu\npanettuſchi/ es juhs ne nokautu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us Jete\nru ſawu Pirindſintu: zellees/no\nkanji tohs / bet taß Puittis ne iſ\nwilke ſawu Sohbinu / jo wiſſe\nbihjajahs/ tapehz ka wiꞥſch wel\njauns bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sebus un Za-\nmunus: zellees tu/ un nahz pat\nmunus / jo kahds Wihrs / tahd\nirr winna Spehks / tad zehlah\nGideans / un nokawe Sebu u\nZalmunu/un zehme tahs Spra-\ndses / kaß apfahrt winno Kame-\ntu Rakleem bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Iſraeta Wih-\nPpp 3\n"
    }
  ],
